{"tid":1021264,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中學比人欺凌過既人入一入黎","createTime":"2019-02-14T06:51:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-14T10:22:44.000Z","uid":5649,"like":10,"dislike":32,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"ba06e8b0dc1b6d1ecc96a40a18383d688c22ba64","tid":1021264,"uid":5649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-14T06:51:29.000Z","msg":"你無問題唔會比人恰架喎<br />\n比人恰多數幾個原因<br />\n1）嘴賤、報串撚、正義撚<br />\n2）樣柒<br />\n3）肥<br />\n4）大陸西<br />\n5）講野口疾疾<br />\n<br />\n多於二項多數會比人打<br />\n多於四項應該連老師都唔鍾意你<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n如果你想話你只係自卑毒撚，自卑毒撚係唔會比人恰，摺友不嬲比人無視<br />\n你諗下自己衰邊飯啦<br />\n上面幾種你唔改善，出到社會一樣比人暗啞底歧視"},{"pid":"0d4d29809c53735745e9cd9d960d56371be5acc6","tid":1021264,"uid":208726,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-14T06:53:44.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"64f04ea8fac468733c562f28116051bd1de36d98","tid":1021264,"uid":152432,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-14T06:54:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mQZv5sX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmQZv5sX.jpg&h=bb69d19c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a4220d42fe67e9cb0b06010d3086a687ef4641e3","tid":1021264,"uid":218954,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-14T06:56:17.000Z","msg":"喺女仔嘅世界<br />\n欺凌一個人係唔需要理由<br />\n或者咩都係理由<br />\n<br />\n利申受害者<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"84edc0d769902af35a547865f6a5904ccff0c920","tid":1021264,"uid":68944,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-14T06:56:31.000Z","msg":"自卑毒撚多數都中2同5<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d251737f153cb9a5b8918a27f92457fdc0c83839","tid":1021264,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-14T06:57:22.000Z","msg":"正解"},{"pid":"71bd357575e4f7e6120e9b0bb1972a43d0c3b7